To further examine the magnetic ground state, exchange coupling between Mn ions has been investigated using the following Heisenberg Hamiltonian:1H=−∑ijJ1SiSj−∑klJ2SkSl−∑mnJ3SmSn\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
